This Java-based system simulates a grocery store. Key classes include:

Sale: Manages customer purchases and discounts during checkout.
Product: Represents store products with stock tracking.
Inventory: Handles product management and retrieval.
GroceryStoreApp: Main application for loading products and processing customers.
Customer: Represents a customer with name validation.
Cart: Manages customer shopping carts.

Compile Java files.
Run GroceryStoreApp.
Input customer count and follow prompts.

Products loaded from ProductList.txt.
Apply discounts during checkout.
Recursive processing for multiple customers

Available discounts:
15Off
winterSale
